  "architecture_summary": "LLaMA-Adapter freezes the entire LLaMA model and fine-tunes only lightweight learnable adaption prompts plus a zero-initialized attention mechanism with learnable gating. It is extended to multi-modal instruction following by adding a frozen image encoder and a learnable projection network, and the same zero-initialized attention idea is also applied to ViT, RoBERTa, and CLIP.",
